OL,3,CRichard Holden's exit from region he
OL,4,Cclaimed to be 'bloody loyal' to
OL,6,FThere was always a risk around Richard
OL,7,FHolden's appointment as Conservative
OL,8,Fparty chairman, given he didn't have a
OL,9,Fseat to stand in at the general
OL,10,Felection.
OL,12,FBy the time he got that cabinet role
OL,13,Flast November, it had already been
OL,14,Fconfirmed that the North West Durham
OL,15,Fconstituency he'd represented since
OL,16,F2019 was being abolished under the
OL,17,Findependent national boundary review,
OL,18,Fwhich has made MPs' seats more equal
OL,19,Fin terms of population size.
