OL,3,CRichard Holden's exit from region he
OL,4,Cclaimed to be 'bloody loyal' to
OL,6,FThat constituency has been portioned
OL,7,Foff into four neighbouring seats -
OL,8,FBlaydon and Consett, Bishop Auckland,
OL,9,FCity of Durham and North Durham - but
OL,10,FMr Holden did not put himself forward
OL,11,Fto be the Conservative candidate in
OL,12,Fany of them.
OL,14,FI asked him about that in February,
OL,15,Fand his reasoning was: "I don't want
OL,16,Fto represent just a part of North West
OL,17,FDurham."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
