OL,3,CRichard Holden's exit from region he
OL,4,Cclaimed to be 'bloody loyal' to
OL,6,FWhen I suggested he was looking for a
OL,7,Fsafer seat elsewhere in the country,
OL,8,Frather than being loyal to the region,
OL,9,Fhe responded: "I am bloody loyal to
OL,10,Fthe North East."
OL,12,FThen last week, with the general
OL,13,Felection having been called early and
OL,14,Fthe deadline for selecting candidates
OL,15,Fapproaching, it emerged that Mr Holden
OL,16,Fwas the only name on the list for
OL,17,Flocal party members to choose from in
OL,18,FBasildon and Billericay.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
