OL,3,CRichard Holden's exit from region he
OL,4,Cclaimed to be 'bloody loyal' to
OL,6,FThat's 300 miles south of his old
OL,7,Fconstituency, and is seen as a safe
OL,8,Fseat for the Conservatives, as they
OL,9,Fwon by more than 20,000 votes there in
OL,10,F2019.
OL,12,FThe old MP had also long confirmed he
OL,13,Fwas standing down at this election.
OL,15,FThe impression that Mr Holden had been
OL,16,Fparachuted in has drawn real anger
OL,17,Ffrom local Conservatives and (unnamed)
OL,18,FTory MP candidates elsewhere, but he
OL,19,Fwas confirmed as the party's candidate
OL,20,Fin Essex.
