OL,3,CRichard Holden's exit from region he
OL,4,Cclaimed to be 'bloody loyal' to
OL,6,FQuestioned by Channel 4 News over his
OL,7,Fprevious assertion of loyalty to the
OL,8,FNorth East, he said: "I stopped being
OL,9,Fthe MP for North West Durham... when
OL,10,Fparliament was dissolved."
OL,12,FThen on Sunday, Mr Holden was made
OL,13,Favailable for a 'pool' interview (a
OL,14,Fnormal practice whereby one
OL,15,Fbroadcaster does an interview and
OL,16,Fothers can also use it).
OL,18,FHe was and repeatedly answered by
OL,19,Fattacking Labour over a shadow
OL,20,Fminister's comments on school class
OL,21,Fsizes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
