OL,6,FAs party chairman, Richard Holden is
OL,7,Fmeant to be a key campaigner and media
OL,8,F'attack dog'.
OL,10,FBut now, in the thick of the election
OL,11,Fcampaign, he's unlikely to be offered
OL,12,Fup for many more interviews in the
OL,13,Fcoming days and weeks.
OL,15,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,16,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,17,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,18,Fdominating the political agenda...
